<h3 style='margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:12.0pt;margin-left:
0cm;line-height:normal'><a name="_Toc426638143"></a><a name="_Toc387761926"><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.5pt'>4.2.7 </span></a><span style='font-size:
10.5pt;font-family:幼圆'>首人常开</span></h3>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:7.8pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:7.8pt;
margin-left:0cm'><b><span style='font-family:幼圆'>首人常开</span></b><span
style='font-family:幼圆'>：在指定时间段，具有首人常开权限的人员验证通过后，门将常开，有效时间段结束后门自动关闭。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:7.8pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:7.8pt;
margin-left:0cm'><span style='font-family:幼圆'>用户可以对具体的门设置首人常开</span><span
lang=EN-US>(</span><span style='font-family:幼圆'>包含门、开门的时间段和具有首人常开的人员</span><span
lang=EN-US>)</span><span style='font-family:幼圆'>。一个门可以设置多个时间段内的首人常开。每个门的页面上会显示当前已存在的首人常开数量。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:7.8pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:7.8pt;
margin-left:0cm'><span style='font-family:幼圆'>新增或者编辑首人常开时，只需要选择门和时间段。记录添加成功后，再添加开门人员。页面右侧可浏览或删除该首人常开设置中的开门人员。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:7.8pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:7.8pt;
margin-left:0cm'><b><span style='font-family:幼圆'>操作步骤如下</span></b><span
style='font-family:幼圆'>：</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:7.8pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:7.8pt;
margin-left:0cm'><span lang=EN-US>1. </span><span style='font-family:幼圆'>点击【门禁】</span><span
lang=EN-US style='font-family:Wingdings'>à</span><span style='font-family:幼圆'>【首人常开】，显示首人常开设置页面。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:7.8pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:7.8pt;
margin-left:0cm'><span lang=EN-US>2. </span><span style='font-family:幼圆'>点击【新增】，选择首人常开的门名称及门常开时间段，点击【确定】保存。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:7.8pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:7.8pt;
margin-left:0cm'><span lang=EN-US>3. </span><span style='font-family:幼圆'>点击</span><span
lang=EN-US>“</span><span style='font-family:幼圆'>操作</span><span lang=EN-US>”</span><span
style='font-family:幼圆'>下的【添加人员】，添加具有首人常开权限的人员（该人员必须具有门禁权限），点击【确定】保存。</span><a
name="_6.3.3_多卡开门"></a></p>

